{"id": "1524466039105130720", "channel_id": "1516880261097328872", "author_id": "1101810380143067166", "author_name": "_lysnthr", "content": "Hello everyone!! This is my first Morimens fanart of our beloved keepers. It took me awhile to finish since I want the art to be close to the game visuals, but I enjoy the process and fell in love with this art style.\n\nI do not know if the keepers are canon in one's timeline or not, but I want to imagine them together for even a short time; thus, it inspired me to draw this. \n\nI will be making more fan art of them in the future and would love to share it here. That's all for me. ₊˚⊹♡", "timestamp": "2026-07-08T17:23:46.932000+00:00", "thread_id": "1516880261097328872"}
